As inflation and volatile markets continue to bleed the value of your cash =
and investments, it might be time to look for a potential solution, outside=
 of traditional markets. One thing I=E2=80=99m looking at are real assets.=
=C2=A0
Why real assets? For inflation protection, historical performance, and port=
folio diversification. According to new research from Goldman Sachs, portfo=
lios with real assets have actually outperformed the 60/40 portfolio since =
WWII.=C2=A0
Right now, one real asset in my portfolio that's in the green is blue-chip =
art. Afterall, if there=E2=80=99s one thing Powell can=E2=80=99t print, it'=
s more Picassos. How am I doing it? With the awarding-winning platform, Mas=
terworks.=C2=A0
Masterworks actually makes it simple to invest in art. For one, they=E2=80=
=99ve built a world-class team of art market professionals who understand t=
his world way better than I do. What I also love is they=E2=80=99re extreme=
ly data driven, and use a proprietary price database to identify artist mom=
entum.=C2=A0
They select works by the same world-renowned artists that are coveted by ul=
tra-wealthy collectors and major museums alike (think Picasso, Basquiat, an=
d Banksy) then securitize them so you can invest. They=E2=80=99ve also deli=
vered solid results, including a 33% net return with their last sale.
